## 통화 관련 Domain Entity

### 예상되는 Call 도메인 Entity 구조

```
domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/call/

├── CallEntity.kt
│   ├── id: String (UUID)
│   ├── callerId: String (FK to UserEntity)
│   ├── calleeId: String (FK to UserEntity)
│   ├── status: Int (INITIATED=0, RINGING=1, ACTIVE=2, COMPLETED=3, FAILED=4)
│   ├── initiatedAt: LocalDateTime
│   ├── startedAt: LocalDateTime?
│   ├── endedAt: LocalDateTime?
│   ├── durationSeconds: Long
│   └── createdAt, updatedAt
│
├── CallRecordEntity.kt
│   ├── id: String (UUID)
│   ├── callId: String (FK to CallEntity)
│   ├── callerId: String
│   ├── calleeId: String
│   ├── durationSeconds: Long
│   ├── reason: String? (COMPLETED, REJECTED, TIMEOUT, etc.)
│   └── metadata: JSON (통화 정보)
│
├── CallRatingEntity.kt
│   ├── id: String (UUID)
│   ├── callRecordId: String (FK)
│   ├── ratedBy: String (FK to UserEntity)
│   ├── ratedTo: String (FK to UserEntity)
│   ├── rating: Int (1-5)
│   ├── comment: String?
│   └── createdAt
│
└── Enum (통화 상태)
    ├── CallStatus
    │   ├── INITIATED (0)
    │   ├── RINGING (1)
    │   ├── ACTIVE (2)
    │   ├── COMPLETED (3)
    │   ├── FAILED (4)
    │   ├── REJECTED (5)
    │   └── TIMEOUT (6)
    │
    └── CallEndReason
        ├── COMPLETED
        ├── REJECTED
        ├── TIMEOUT
        ├── USER_CANCELLED
        └── NETWORK_ERROR
```

### 주요 엔티티 구현 예시

**CallEntity**:
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "call")
class CallEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    val callerId: String,
    val calleeId: String,

    @Column(nullable = false)
    var status: Int = CallStatus.INITIATED.value,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var initiatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    var startedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
    var endedAt: LocalDateTime? = null,
    var durationSeconds: Long? = null,

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

**CallRepository**:
```kotlin
interface CallRepository : JpaRepository<CallEntity, String> {
    fun findByCallerId(callerId: String): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByCallerIdAndStatus(callerId: String, status: Int): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByCalleeIdAndStatus(calleeId: String, status: Int): List<CallEntity>
    fun findByIdAndStatus(id: String, status: Int): Optional<CallEntity>
}
```

### Catalog 매핑

| Catalog | 도메인 |
|---------|--------|
| `maum` | user, profile, call, product, follow |
| `moment` | post, moment, comment, like |
| `chat` | chat_room |
| `notification` | notification, notification_setting |

Call 엔티티는 `maum` catalog에 속함.

