## Proto/gRPC 패턴

### Proto 파일 위치 및 구조

```
protobuf/src/main/proto/

├── user/
│   └── user.proto
├── call/
│   └── call.proto
├── chat/
│   └── chat.proto
└── ...
```

### Call gRPC Proto 예시

**protobuf/src/main/proto/call/call.proto**:

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package call;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.call";

// ============ Service ============
service CallService {
  rpc InitiateCall(InitiateCallRequest) returns (InitiateCallResponse);
  rpc EndCall(EndCallRequest) returns (EndCallResponse);
  rpc GetCallStatus(GetCallStatusRequest) returns (GetCallStatusResponse);
  rpc ListCallRecords(ListCallRecordsRequest) returns (ListCallRecordsResponse);
  rpc RateCall(RateCallRequest) returns (RateCallResponse);
}

// ============ Requests ============
message InitiateCallRequest {
  string caller_id = 1;
  string callee_id = 2;
}

message EndCallRequest {
  string call_id = 1;
  int64 duration_seconds = 2;
}

message GetCallStatusRequest {
  string call_id = 1;
}

message ListCallRecordsRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  int32 limit = 2;
  int32 offset = 3;
}

message RateCallRequest {
  string call_record_id = 1;
  string rated_by = 2;
  string rated_to = 3;
  int32 rating = 4;
  string comment = 5;
}

// ============ Responses ============
message InitiateCallResponse {
  Call call = 1;
}

message EndCallResponse {
  Call call = 1;
}

message GetCallStatusResponse {
  Call call = 1;
}

message ListCallRecordsResponse {
  repeated CallRecord records = 1;
  int32 total = 2;
}

message RateCallResponse {
  CallRating rating = 1;
}

// ============ Models ============
message Call {
  string id = 1;
  string caller_id = 2;
  string callee_id = 3;
  int32 status = 4;  // 0:INITIATED, 1:RINGING, 2:ACTIVE, 3:COMPLETED, 4:FAILED
  string initiated_at = 5;
  string started_at = 6;
  string ended_at = 7;
  int64 duration_seconds = 8;
}

message CallRecord {
  string id = 1;
  string call_id = 2;
  string caller_id = 3;
  string callee_id = 4;
  int64 duration_seconds = 5;
  string reason = 6;
}

message CallRating {
  string id = 1;
  string call_record_id = 2;
  string rated_by = 3;
  string rated_to = 4;
  int32 rating = 5;
  string comment = 6;
  string created_at = 7;
}
```

### Proto 컨벤션

| 항목 | 규칙 |
|------|------|
| 패키지 | 도메인명 (소문자): `call`, `user` |
| 서비스명 | `{Domain}Service`: `CallService` |
| 메서드명 | 동작형: `GetCallStatus`, `InitiateCall`, `ListCallRecords` |
| 필드명 | `snake_case`: `caller_id`, `duration_seconds` |
| Request/Response | `{Method}Request`, `{Method}Response` |
| Message 필드 번호 | 1부터 순차 증가, **절대 재사용 금지** |

### Proto 빌드

```bash
# Proto 컴파일
./gradlew :protobuf:clean :protobuf:build

# 생성 파일
# protobuf/build/generated/source/proto/main/java/
#   └── com/maum/backend/protobuf/call/
#       ├── CallServiceGrpc.java
#       ├── InitiateCallRequest.java
#       └── ... (모든 Message 클래스)
```

